      <para styleclass="Heading1">6: Memo</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="6r.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Heading2" style="font-size:14pt; vertical-align:baseline;" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Heading2"> Memo dialog-box</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The memo is a <text styleclass="Body Text" style="font-style:italic;">Windows NotePad®</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> style interface</text>. The <text styleclass="Interface">Model-Editor</text> and<text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"> each </text><text styleclass="Interface">Mechanism-Editor</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"> can have their own memo. </text><text styleclass="Body Text">The memo is saved with the model file.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><table styleclass="Standard" rowcount="1" colcount="2">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:291px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="Dialog-13.2-Memo.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">To open a memo:</para>
          <list id="0" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Numbered" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Numbered"><text style="font-style:normal;">Right-click</text>&#32;<text styleclass="Interface">Model name-tab</text> or <text styleclass="Interface">Mechanism name-tab</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
            <li styleclass="HowTo Numbered"><text style="font-style:normal;">Click</text>&#32;<text styleclass="T_Menu">Open Memo</text> in the contextual-menu</li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">To stop the memo opening when you start <text styleclass="VariableName-IT" translate="false">MechDesigner</text><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;">:</text></para>
          <list id="1" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Numbered" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo Numbered">Clear the <text styleclass="VariableName-IT">&apos;Automatically Open on Start&apos;</text> check-box, at the bottom of the <text styleclass="Element">Memo dialog</text><image src="Red-14-1b.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Body Text" style="font-weight:bold;">.</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
